name: playerCount
description: The Number of players participating in the given game.

name: numRounds
description: The number of rounds played in the game.

name: showNRounds
description: Is the total number of rounds shown to players?

name: endowment
description: The coins given to players at the beginning of each round.

name: multiplier
description: The multiplying factor of the total contributions to the public fund.

name: allOrNothing
description: Are players only allowed to contribute/withhold the entire endowment?

name: chat
description: Can players chat with each other?

name: defaultContribProp
description: The proportion of the endowment contributed to the fund by default.

name: punishmentExists
description: Can players punish?

name: punishmentCost
description: The number of coins it costs to impose a single punishment.

name: punishmentMagnitude
description: The number of coins deducted per punishment inflicted.

name: rewardExists
description: Can players reward?

name: rewardCost
description: The number of coins it costs to grant a single reward.

name: rewardMagnitude
description: The number of coins added per reward granted.

name: showOtherSummaries
description: Can players see the summaries of other players?

name: showPunishmentId
description: Can players see who punished them?

name: showRewardId
description: Can players see who rewarded them?

name: contributionDuration
description: The length of the contribution phase, in seconds.

name: outcomeDuration
description: The length of the outcome phase, in seconds.

name: summaryDuration
description: The length of the summary phase, in seconds.

name: basePay
description: The base pay given to participants, in USD.

name: conversionRate
description: The rate of exchange from coins to USD.
